tnotes}}\n| population_total = {{Austria population Wikidata|population_total}}\n| population_urban =  \n| population_metro =  \n| population_note  = \n| population_density_km2 = auto\n| established_title = \n| established_date  = \n| timezone          = [[Central European Time|CET]]\n| timezone_DST      = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset        = +1\n| utc_offset_DST    = +2\n| registration_plate = [[Vehicle registration plates of Austria|JO]]\n| postal_code_type   = [[List of postal codes in Austria|Postal code]]\n| postal_code        = 5603\n| area_code_type = [[Telephone numbers in Austria|Area code]]\n| area_code      = 06418\n| website   = [http://www.kleinarl.at/ www.kleinarl.at]\n| footnotes = \n}}\n'''Kleinarl''' is a municipality in the [[St. Johann im Pongau (district)|St. Johann im Pongau district]] in the [[Austria]]n state of [[Salzburg (state)|Salzburg]].\n\n==Geography==\n[[File:Kirche-Kleinarl1.jpg|thumb|left|Parish church]]\nThe municipal area is located in the Pongau region within the [[Central Eastern Alps]], on the northern rim of the [[High Tauern]] national park. The [[Radstadt Tauern]] mountain range with the source of the [[Enns (river)|Enns]] river separates it from the Salzburg [[Tamsweg District|Lungau]] region. In the south, it borders on the market town of [[Wagrain]].\n\nThe ''Flachauwinkl\u2013Kleinarl'' ski area is part of the [[Ski Amad\u00e9]] network. The inhabitants mainly depend on winter tourism, but hiking and cycling in summer is also popular.\n\n==History==\nThe [[Gothic architecture|Gothic]] St. Lawrence parish church was consecrated in 1443. It was rebuilt from 1984 to 1986 according to plans by [[Heinz Tesar]]. The [[Archbishopric of Salzburg|Prince-Archbishops of Salzburg]] had a hunting lodge erected at Kleinarl, which since the mid 18th century serves as a vicarage.\n \n===Population===\n{{Historical populations\n|align=left\n|1971|593\n|1981|651\n|1991|724\n|2001|743\n|2010|783 \n}}\n{{clear-left}}\n\n==Notable people==\n*[[Annemarie Moser-Pr\u00f6ll]] (born 1953), skier\n*[[Cornelia Pr\u00f6ll]] (born 1961), skier.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat|Kleinarl}}\n*[http://www.kleinarl.at/system/web/default.aspx Municipal site] {{in lang|de}}\n*[http://www.wagrain-kleinarl.at/en/summer.html Wagrain-Kleinarl tourist site]\n{{wikivoyage-inline}}\n\n{{Cities and towns in St. Johann im Pongau (district)}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in St. Johann im Pongau District]]\n\n{{Salzburg-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kleinarl"}
