ST]]\n| utc_offset        = +1\n| utc_offset_DST    = +2\n| registration_plate = \n| postal_code_type   = [[List of postal codes in Austria|Postal code]]\n| postal_code        = 9753\n| area_code_type = [[Telephone numbers in Austria|Area code]]\n| area_code      = 04768\n| website   = \n| footnotes = \n}}\n\n'''Kleblach-Lind''' is a town in the district of [[Spittal an der Drau (district)|Spittal an der Drau]] in the [[Austria]]n state of [[Carinthia (state)|Carinthia]].\n\n==Geography==\nKleblach-Lind lies on the east end of the upper Drau valley, about 10&nbsp;km as the crow flies from [[Spittal an der Drau]]. The two towns are separated only by the Drau.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{commons|Kleblach-Lind}}\n{{Cities and towns in Spittal an der Drau (district)}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Spittal an der Drau District]]\n\n\n{{Carinthia-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name            = Kleblach-Lind\n| native_name     = \n| settlement_type = \n<!-- Images     -->\n| image_skyline   = \n| imagesize       = \n| image_caption   = \n| image_shield    = Wappen at kleblach-lind.png\n| shield_size     = 80x110px\n| shield_link     = \n<!-- Maps           -->\n| pushpin_map         = Austria\n| pushpin_mapsize     = 270\n| pushpin_map_caption = Location within Austria\n| image_map           = \n| mapsize             = \n| map_alt             =\n| map_caption         = Location within [[Spittal an der Drau (district)|Spittal an der Drau]] district\n<!-- Location    -->\n| coordinates       = {{coord|46|46|N|13|21|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type  = Country\n| subdivision_name  = [[Austria]]\n| subdivision_type1 = [[States of Austria|State]]\n| subdivision_name1 = [[Carinthia]]\n| subdivision_type2 = [[District (Austria)|District]]\n| subdivision_name2 = [[Spittal an der Drau (district)|Spittal an der Drau]]\n| parts_type        = \n| parts_style       = para\n| p1                = \n<!-- Leaders -->\n