esz-KDNP-Nagykun Civilian Circle).\n\nThe local Municipal Assembly, elected at the [[2019 Hungarian local elections|2019 local government elections]], is made up of 11 members (1 Mayor, 8 Individual constituencies MEPs and 3 Compensation List MEPs) divided into this political parties and alliances:<ref>{{cite web|title=V\u00e1rosi k\u00f6zgy\u0171l\u00e9s tagjai 2019-2024 - Kis\u00fajsz\u00e1ll\u00e1s (J\u00e1sz-Nagykun-Szolnok megye)|url=https://www.valasztas.hu/telepules-adatlap_onk2019?_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_formDate=32503680000000&p_p_id=onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet&p_p_lifecycle=1&p_p_state=normal&p_p_mode=view&p_p_col_id=column-2&p_p_col_pos=1&p_p_col_count=5&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpVlId=294&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpVltId=687&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpMegyeKod=11&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpTelepulesKod=031&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_settlement=kis%C3%BAjsz%C3%A1ll%C3%A1s|agency=valasztas.hu|accessdate=2019-10-29}}</ref>\n\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" class=\"wikitable\"\n! style=\"background:#ccc\" colspan=\"2\" | Party\n! style=\"background:#ccc\" | Seats\n! style=\"background:#ccc\" colspan=\"9\" | Current Municipal Assembly\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}}  | &nbsp;\n|[[Fidesz]]-[[Christian Democratic People's Party (Hungary)|KDNP]]-Nagykun Civilian Circle\n| style=\"text-align: right\" | '''9'''\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} |<span style=\"color:white;\">'''M'''</span>\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|-\n|